		{
			title: "The \"Useful in Multiplayer\" Terminal"
			x: 2.5d
			y: 6.5d
			subtitle: "My Server. My Rules. Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"The Security Terminal will unlock the ability to use Wireless Terminals with your ME System. These will allow for long range access to the system."
				""
				"It will also allow you to configure which users, and what permissions the users have with the ME System. By existing it enforces permissions on the usage of the system."
				""
				"By default, the Security Terminal does not prevent tampering with your system. Destructive, removing cables/machines or breaking of drives is not directly provided by the Terminal. If you need to protect your system from physical vandalism you will need another form of physical security. This block provides Network level security."
				""
				"The player who places the ME Security Terminal has full control over the network and cannot exclude himself any rights. By adding a blank Biometric Card you define a default behavior for every player who has no own Biometric Card registered."
				""
				"{image:kubejs:textures/ae2/security_terminal_example.png width:110 height:100 align:1 fit:true}"
			]
			hide_dependency_lines: false
			dependencies: ["041F7FE086B9E43D"]
