			subtitle: "Shulker+ Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"The Personal Chest is a form of storage added by Mekanism. Once you obtain it, you'll have to right-click with it in your hand to assign it to yourself."
				""
				"After that, you can simply access its inventory (which is as large as one vanilla double chest) by right-clicking the air. To place it down, just shift right-click a block. You can configure its security settings to allow certain players to access it or not."
