			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "Mark V - No, it does not come in a suitcase. The Fifth Tier Backpack is made with 1 Netherite Ingot and it will provide 96 Slots. It will also have 4 Upgrade Slots"
			dependencies: [
				"61640A55E9877F54"
